3 A model with heavy quarks and light diquarks The model we are proposing treats the two light quarks within the heavy baryons as effectively propagating scalar and axial vector pointlike diquarks. This is sufficient to obtain a dynamics that respects chiral and heavy quark symmetry. The model lagrangian reads

L = L0 + L1 + L2 ; (21)L

